Refer to the pages

http://wapiti.limsi.fr/manual.html#patterns
http://crfpp.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/doc/index.html#templ


**IMPORTANT**
If you added shape or lexicon features, you should change the feature list 
in Extact::_printdataWapiti. Then add template of unigram in pattern_ref.
For example, if you added 14th group of features in the feature list 
in Extact::_printdataWapiti, activate U139:%x[-1,14], U140:%x[0,14], 
U141:%x[1,14] by deleting '#' at the very front. If you agin add 15th
group of features, add U149:%x[-1,15], U150:%x[0,15], U151:%x[1,15].

